movies.title: Elisa & Marcela
movies.plot: In 1901, Marcela Gracia Ibeas took on the identity of Mario Sánchez to marry her lover of fifteen years, Elisa Sanchez Loriga.

events.title: Marcela Gracia Ibeas, using a fake male identity of "Mario", marries Elisa Sánchez Loriga, the first same sex marriage in Spain since the Roman Empire
